---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import MetricCard from "../../components/MetricCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>

<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

<!-- HEADER -->

<header class="mb-14">

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
May 2023 — Present
</p>

<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
Backend Developer
</h1>

<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
Backend developer working on SaaS products in the tourism sector,
including PMS, Channel Manager and booking engines managing more
than <strong class="text-blue-600">2 million reservations per year</strong>.
</p>

</header>


<!-- ABOUT -->

<section class="mb-14">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
About the role
</h2>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
I work on backend systems that support business-critical SaaS products
used by hotels and tourism companies. The platform processes large
amounts of reservations, billing operations and third-party integrations.
</p>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
My daily work focuses on evolving legacy systems towards cleaner
architectures using principles such as SOLID, Domain Driven Design
and Hexagonal Architecture.
</p>

</section>


<!-- PROJECT 1 -->

<section class="mb-16">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">
Electronic Invoicing SaaS
</h2>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
Development of a unified invoicing system that consolidates billing
from three independent products: hotel PMS, activity management
software and internal management systems.

The module also implements electronic invoicing integrations for
multiple countries and administrations.
</p>


<!-- METRICS -->

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">

<MetricCard
value="+5000"
label="invoices generated per day"
/>

<MetricCard
value="3"
label="billing domains unified"
/>

<MetricCard
value="6"
label="electronic billing integrations"
/>

</div>


<!-- DETAILS -->

<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 list-disc pl-6">

<li>TicketBai integration for the Basque Country (Araba, Bizkaia and Gipuzkoa)</li>

<li>VeriFactu integration for Spain</li>

<li>SWSapien integration for Mexico</li>

<li>Architecture designed to support new regulatory integrations</li>

</ul>

</section>



<!-- PROJECT 2 -->

<section class="mb-16">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">
Electronic Lock Integrations
</h2>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
Development of integrations with multiple smart lock providers used
by hotels and short-term rentals. The system allows automated
check-ins and secure access management for guests.
</p>


<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">

<MetricCard
value="7"
label="lock providers integrated"
/>

<MetricCard
value="API"
label="REST integrations"
/>

<MetricCard
value="Async"
label="event-driven processes"
/>

</div>


<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 list-disc pl-6">

<li>Integrations with TTLock, Nuki, Tesa, Yacan, Padword, Omnitec and Akiles</li>

<li>Decoupled architecture supporting multiple providers</li>

<li>Event-driven processes ensuring system consistency</li>

</ul>

</section>



<!-- PROJECT 3 -->

<section class="mb-16">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">
Activity Channel Manager
</h2>

<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
Refactoring and evolution of the activity distribution system,
integrating major tourism distribution platforms.
</p>


<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">

<MetricCard
value="5"
label="distribution platforms"
/>

<MetricCard
value="Millions"
label="reservations processed"
/>

<MetricCard
value="Full"
label="system refactor"
/>

</div>


<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 list-disc pl-6">

<li>Integrations with Civitatis, GetYourGuide, Viator, Tiqets (OCTO) and Axess</li>

<li>Refactoring applying Clean Code and Hexagonal Architecture</li>

<li>Improved maintainability and scalability</li>

</ul>

</section>



<!-- TECH -->

<section>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
Technologies
</h2>

<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">PHP 8+</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">Laravel</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">MySQL</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">Docker</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">Vue.js</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">DDD</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">Hexagonal Architecture</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">TDD</span>

<span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm">REST / SOAP APIs</span>

</div>

</section>

</article>

</BaseLayout>